<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><span title="Pronunciation in IPA" class="IPA">[t̪əmɨɻ] <a href="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/05/Tamil.ogg" class="internal" title="Tamil.ogg">(Listen)</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
